to build and run the system all you need to do is the follwoing
1. Prerequisites
Make sure you have the following installed on your system:

- A GCC compiler (gcc)
- make utility
- konsole terminal emulator
- Development libraries for ncurses (if required by your system)
- Fastssd installed

2. make sure that launcher.sh has executable permission 
	- if it don't have just run chmod +x launcher.sh

3. from terminal run ./launcher.sh
	- the launcher file will build the system by the make file
	- do some initilization
	- start all nodes

4. just play and have fun !!
